Output assets/synrail-false-green-hero.gif
Output assets/synrail-false-green-hero.mp4

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1500
Set Height 760
Set TypingSpeed 35ms
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 42

Hide
Type "unset NO_COLOR; export SYNRAIL_DEMO_COLOR=1; clear"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Show
Type "./run_demo.sh"
Enter
Sleep 8s
